&lt;p&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/p&gt;

&lt;div&gt;Well, this is unfortunate, but in lieu of knowing a better alternative, I&#39;d probably be in favor of just sticking it out..&nbsp;
&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;Email functionality will remain intact. We don&#39;t tend to share files/photos very often on this list, and when we do, I thought it tended to be via links to repositories or the websites of research groups (correct me if I&#39;m wrong).&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;I don&#39;t think Google Groups is a very good alternative, either. If someone has suggestions, please share.&lt;/div&gt;

&lt;div&gt;&nbsp;&lt;/div&gt;
&lt;/div&gt;
&nbsp;

