&lt;div id=&quot;gmail-m_-523900770739615365ygrp-text&quot;&gt;
&lt;p&gt;My understanding is that the email list functionality will remain, for&lt;br/&gt;
the time being anyways, but any uploaded/attached files will be&lt;br/&gt;
deleted, all or most of the other functionality available via the web&lt;br/&gt;
site will be gone, and the group will become a private group.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Seems to me to be a clear signal to move elsewhere - any suggestions?&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Google groups seems like the obvious choice, but I mostly agree with&lt;br/&gt;
Sean&#39;s comments - it will likely get culled at some point too.&lt;br/&gt;
&lt;br/&gt;
Colin&lt;br/&gt;
